message.content:
1. Two studies were conducted.
2. LDX was tested in these studies.
3. OROS-MPH was tested in these studies.
4. Placebo was used as a control in these studies.
5. LDX was found to be superior to placebo in all efficacy-related endpoints.
6. OROS-MPH was found to be superior to placebo in all efficacy-related endpoints.
7. The p-value for all efficacy-related endpoints was less than 0.0001.
8. The effect size (ES) range for all efficacy-related endpoints was between -0.43 to -1.16.

messages.content:
Statement: In both studies, LDX and OROS-MPH were superior to placebo for all efficacy-related endpoints (all nominal p < 0.0001; ES range −0.43 to −1.16).

List all the facts we explicitly know from the statement. Make each fact as atomic as possible.
